snippet.textDisplay:
Writing this from core of my heart. ❤ I listened to this song for the first time in Balika Vadhu and was mesmerized by this song. But back then we didn't had smartphones or music streaming options to listen songs...so I used to watch the serial every day at 8pm. 'Balika Vadhu' is a serial which will always be close to my heart. Its characters, Bg songs and everything just reminds me of my innocent childhood.

Today when I am writing this, we have lost "Shiv" hamare sabke Collector saab. Back then Siddharth Shukla's character was an epitome of handsomeness, Polite nature, a successful man. I whenever watched that seriel, looked upto Shiv.


Sadly we lost Pratyusha long back and now Siddharth. This song will always and always remind me of our Shiv and Anandi, our Pratyusha and Siddharth !!  

Hope they are happy in the abode of heaven and we will always keep u both in our hearts. And specially this song will always and always remind us of you both.



Love you Shiv and Anandi
Om shanti Siddharth Shukla 🙏🏻
